/8e19/787b/382839_large.png?m=1636944229", "created": 1549853805, "last_modified": 1636944229}, "last_reply_by": "gadore", "last_touched": 1701397539, "title": "分享一下今年提升幸福感最强的两样东西", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/996539", "created": 1701326955, "deleted": 0, "content": "一个是把自己的 iPhone12pro 换成了二手的 13pro max ，续航瞬间拉满了，可能是用的太久，12pro 续航太差了，满格电玩不了一上午，在地铁上面玩一个小时就只有 60%的电，自从换了 13pm 之后就再也没有续航焦虑\r\n\r\n\r\n另外一个就是把之前住的单间换成了主卧独卫的单间，多了一个卫生间，房租 1000 变成了 1300 ，想什么时候洗澡都可以，也不怕忘记带毛巾了，感觉自己最近胖了也是重新锻炼起来", "content_rendered": "<p>一个是把自己的 iPhone12pro 换成了二手的 13pro max ，续航瞬间拉满了，可能是用的太久，12pro 续航太差了，满格电玩不了一上午，在地铁上面玩一个小时就只有 60%的电，自从换了 13pm 之后就再也没有续航焦虑</p>\n<p>另外一个就是把之前住的单间换成了主卧独卫的单间，多了一个卫生间，房租 1000 变成了 1300 ，想什么时候洗澡都可以，也不怕忘记带毛巾了，感觉自己最近胖了也是重新锻炼起来</p>\n", "last_modified": 1701326982, "replies": 84, "id": 996539}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 5220, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 1297, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 140222, "username": "a134698815", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/a134698815", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5878fca1468a42cbbffa9c7aa8819f5f?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5878fca1468a42cbbffa9c7aa8819f5f?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5878fca1468a42cbbffa9c7aa8819f5f?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1443329606, "last_modified": 1443329606}, "last_reply_by": "bigshawn", "last_touched": 1701404175, "title": "12 月了，一年又见底了，大家都过得怎样呢？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/996699", "created": 1701390172, "deleted": 0, "content": "去年 10 月登陆澳洲，老婆读书，我陪读。\r\n\r\n去年 12 月-3 月，在一家巴西老板小外包公司被 pua 到怀疑自我，精神差点崩溃，然后离职。\r\n\r\n4-5 月，调整心态后重新找工作，拿到两个 offer ，一个博彩相关，两周上 9 天班，拒了。一个区块链相关，接了。\r\n\r\n6-12 月，努力工作，争取下周通过试用期。\r\n\r\n现在仍然不想回顾起上半年的经历，太离谱了，好在下半年都在慢慢变好。\r\n\r\n都会越来越好的不是吗？", "content_rendered": "<p>去年 10 月登陆澳洲，老婆读书，我陪读。</p>\n<p>去年 12 月-3 月，在一家巴西老板小外包公司被 pua 到怀疑自我，精神差点崩溃，然后离职。</p>\n<p>4-5 月，调整心态后重新找工作，拿到两个 offer ，一个博彩相关，两周上 9 天班，拒了。一个区块链相关，接了。</p>\n<p>6-12 月，努力工作，争取下周通过试用期。</p>\n<p>现在仍然不想回顾起上半年的经历，太离谱了，好在下半年都在慢慢变好。</p>\n<p>都会越来越好的不是吗？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1701393688, "replies": 69, "id": 996699}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 212906, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4042, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 112093, "username": "nextbox", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/nextbox", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/02cb/27fa/112093_mini.png?m=1496979972", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/02cb/27fa/112093_normal.png?m=1496979972", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/02cb/27fa/112093_large.png?m=1496979972", "created": 1429526248, "last_modified": 1496979972}, "last_reply_by": "sadfQED2", "last_touched": 1701396921, "title": "看了拼多多 Q3 的财报，大家有什么想说的？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/996619", "created": 1701340146, "deleted": 0, "content": "![]( https://i.imgur.com/J9F7Kcu.png) \r\n 身边的人都在说大环境不好，裁员。\r\n 然而拼多多 Q3 财报逆势而上，大家觉得是什么原因让他逆势而上呢？\r\n \r\n 一直认为拼多多的成功因为优惠的价格(压榨商家、百亿补贴)，但是看到一些观点认为拼多多如今的成功主要不是因为这个优惠政策，那是什么原因呀？\r\n  ![]( https://i.imgur.com/W3JtYWY.png)", "content_rendered": "<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/J9F7Kcu.png\"/>\n身边的人都在说大环境不好，裁员。\n然而拼多多 Q3 财报逆势而上，大家觉得是什么原因让他逆势而上呢？</p>\n<p>一直认为拼多多的成功因为优惠的价格(压榨商家、百亿补贴)，但是看到一些观点认为拼多多如今的成功主要不是因为这个优惠政策，那是什么原因呀？\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W3JtYWY.png\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1701340146, "replies": 59, "id": 996619}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1700771269", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1700771269", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 60104, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1700771269", "stars": 8745, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 212918, "username": "zsvc", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/zsvc", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7a24/2ce0/212918_mini.png?m=1687010154", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7a24/2ce0/212918_normal.png?m=1687010154", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7a24/2ce0/212918_large.png?m=1687010154", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7a24/2ce0/212918_xlarge.png?m=1687010154", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7a24/2ce0/212918_xlarge.png?m=1687010154", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7a24/2ce0/212918_xlarge.png?m=1687010154", "created": 1486096474, "last_modified": 1687010154}, "last_reply_by": "monkeydev", "last_touched": 1701366304, "title": "自建什